    "To ensure the reliability of the analysis, three authors, using TDF, independently annotated one transcript (AA, NA, TF).",
    "An initial coding scheme was then developed based on the discussion of disagreements.",
    "This coding scheme was used to guide the analysis of the remaining transcripts.",
